                <div class="r_rcw_review_text r_rcw_focused_review_text">I ordered a new support like for my camper awning. It came the next day, I was shocked I couldn&#039;t believe it was here that fast. I do live relatively close to the factory at least in the same state anyway. But they were very easy to work with and the part was right and of course an original. Highly recommend the company.</div>

