                    </div>
                            <div class="r_rcw_focused_review_title">
                    Nomadic had a hard-to-find part
                </div>
                <div class="r_rcw_review_text r_rcw_focused_review_text">When the outer clear plastic window on my Dometic Midi-Heki 500x700 skylight was damaged, it was very difficult to find a replacement for this German made part. And, the skylight was leaking in the rain, so I needed it quickly!<br />
<br />
Initially, the only places that appeared to have it were in Germany, UK, Canada and Australia. Luckily, I stumbled onto the Nomadic website, and they had the piece in stock for immediate delivery. Nomadic is the first place I&#039;ll check in the future for hard-to-find Dometic parts and anything else RV-related.</div>

