                </div>
                <div class="r_rcw_review_text r_rcw_focused_review_text">I needed a replacement end cap for the original awning on my 28-year old Chinook RV.  After unsuccessfully spending much time looking elsewhere for this part, I came across Nomadic Supply, who very quickly provided the exact part needed with little effort on my part.  I highly recommend them.</div>

