                <div class="r_rcw_review_text r_rcw_focused_review_text">UPS could not find our new community home.  The part was sent back to the store.  With just one email, the store re-shipped the part via USPS and it was delivered quickly!  Now that is customer service!!!!  Thank you!</div>

