backlighting for the ultimate combination of performance and style. This premium LED light bar transforms your vehicle's lighting setup with seven vibrant backlight colors and RIGID's legendary durability.","author_id":"Instagram|9325069404269180","author_name":"nomadic.supply","media_content":[{"media_type":"image","image_url":"https://scontent-iad3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/659787432_18085007807627543_1865116008927172910_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=104&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=w2vaM0Q7-v4Q7kNvwE56pIT&_nc_oc=AdpRW7LKlV7FZu0SLw9sao3FkI-URob_K5gzOzRIncqYDSM-t1n7upPDqYqqF9fYwP8&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=8oeHHt-Yinuc-ZzrCuQW_w&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQH88p4YYsAn3Bv2t9ecp67Ye3Lhu3FdGtl52ivTGNfv_cg8MPonTwIMREfZ1T2RGw8A2_csp6DIxA&oh=00_Af2v8knBo8chzoXpzfLjz7KyDVWiMRm91KeDcOacBQlfXw&oe=69E3843A","image_urls":{"size":"1000x1000","large":"feed/Instagram/e4/76/e47624660d85c439277827441807b6c2bc4546aa/0.webp","medium":"feed/Instagram/e4/76/e47624660d85c439277827441807b6c2bc4546aa/0m.webp","small":"feed/Instagram/e4/76/e47624660d85c439277827441807b6c2bc4546aa/0s.webp"}}],"created_at":"2026-04-05 16:20:56","source_type":"Instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/p/DWwai_CFaZz/","comment_count":"?","comments":[],"like_count":"?"},{"id":"18001736042879106","source_id":"6240","type":"image","text":"New product from Nomadic Supply Company®! Camco 40460 Powered Camper Van Roof Vent Fan\n\nThe Camco 40460 Powered Camper Van Roof Vent Fan from Nomadic Supply Company® brings fresh air and natural daylight into your RV or camper van through a tinted skylight that filters 80% of sunlight for a relaxed and comfortable interior atmosphere. Featuring three fan modes, four speeds, a 60° oscillating vent, and a smart thermostat that automatically activates in exhaust mode at 78°F, the Camco 40460 Powered Camper Van Roof Vent Fan gives you complete control over your RV’s climate through a mobile app, wireless remote, or intuitive touch panel.","author_id":"Instagram|9325069404269180","author_name":"nomadic.supply","media_content":[{"media_type":"image","image_url":"https://scontent-iad6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/657712290_18084758480627543_3357353792933720256_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=100&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=u2yG19gMlwgQ7kNvwEjO6Xq&_nc_oc=AdpWXdZWyIwxmh21zqEz6Lu7XdalkyYpgxRnpHjkCALANPAdHE0SSC3d191Ur_A1IVo&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-iad6-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=8oeHHt-Yinuc-ZzrCuQW_w&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQGDA9e_JDVso_jPB4iTLPtojXYxfpfZKSbb1Raa4KbVcAxXzJHhWZKScxZ3jhTJ4sPDGKUefsZlRg&oh=00_Af1WSK__gGz4qcyzsAQAWVg_pZK0a0Ig9nEgpF2Wm6qtpw&oe=69E38FA5","image_urls":{"size":"1080x1080","large":"feed/Instagram/4f/7d/4f7d18f8bcbbdaee060de34348a81d16450c899a/0.webp","medium":"feed/Instagram/4f/7d/4f7d18f8bcbbdaee060de34348a81d16450c899a/0m.webp","small":"feed/Instagram/4f/7d/4f7d18f8bcbbdaee060de34348a81d16450c899a/0s.webp"}}],"created_at":"2026-04-03 16:35:45","source_type":"Instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/p/DWrSpbbEqWS/","comment_count":"?","comments":[],"like_count":"?"},{"id":"18132309502534038","source_id":"6240","type":"image","text":"Sometimes taking the long way home is exactly what you need. 🌤️\n\nA few extra minutes. A little quiet. A chance to think.\n\nAre you team shortcut or scenic route? 🚗","author_id":"Instagram|9325069404269180","author_name":"nomadic.supply","media_content":[{"media_type":"image","image_url":"https://scontent-iad6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/657296022_18084394205627543_4836994633351631010_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=106&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=HipbkX96ehkQ7kNvwHtJlt3&_nc_oc=AdqwS8nI--5v3Vdr8OXfgVe6cTOIKIgbPQeIr7rrfaKhv9V2SmC5roYb06uoFzIRt3o&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-iad6-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=8oeHHt-Yinuc-ZzrCuQW_w&_